zh: BigONE Earn 是一款由 BigONE 赚币体系提供支持的机器人
用户可以通过机器人一键参与 BTC、ETH、USDT 等多币种的赚币产品，存取自由，方便快捷，让闲置资金“赚”起来！
en: BigONE Earn is a robot powered by the BigONE earning system.
Users can participate in multi-currency earning products such as BTC, ETH, USDT, etc. with one click of the robot, with free access, convenient and fast, and let idle funds `earn`!
